snippet.title: 【VR】SLASH OF BULLET - Official Game Trailer 【PC】
snippet.description:
An exhilarating VR game with a new sensation where you take down many enemy robots with sword slashes.
(剣を振って斬撃を飛ばし、敵ロボットを切りまくる爽快感抜群の新感覚VRゲーム。)
